'''電壓門控離子通道'''（{{lang-en|Voltage-gated ion channels}}）是一類[[跨膜蛋白|跨膜蛋白]]，在附近的[[膜電位|膜電位]]變化时來可激活形成[[離子通道|離子通道]]。膜電位改變可改变该通道蛋白的構象，來調節其打開和關閉。[[離子|離子]]通常情况下不可滲透[[細胞膜|細胞膜]]，因此它们必须通过跨膜的蛋白通道来穿越细胞膜。通道的打開和關閉是通過改變細胞膜兩側之間的離子濃度以及電荷梯度來觸發的<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Catterall WA | title = From ionic currents to molecular mechanisms: the structure and function of voltage-gated sodium channels | language = en | journal = Neuron | volume = 26 | issue = 1 | pages = 13–25 | date = April 2000 | pmid = 10798388 | doi = 10.1016/S0896-6273(00)81133-2 }}</ref>。

電壓門控離子通道在[[神經細胞|神經細胞]]和[[肌肉組織|肌肉組織]]等興奮性細胞中起著至關重要的作用，可以響應觸發[[電壓|電壓]]變化而快速而協調地進行[[去極化|去極化]]。沿著軸突和突觸處建立的電壓閘門離子通道定向傳播電信號。電壓門控離子通道通常是離子特異性的，现在已經发现了[[鈉離子|鈉離子]]（Na<sup>+</sup>）、[[鉀離子|鉀離子]]（K<sup>+</sup>）、[[鈣離子|鈣離子]]（Ca<sup>2+</sup>）和[[氯離子|氯離子]]（Cl<sup>-</sup>）的通道<ref name="Neuroscience_2001">{{cite book | first1 = Dale | last1 = Purves | first2 = George J | last2 = Augustine | first3 = David | last3 = Fitzpatrick | first4 = Lawrence C | last4 = Katz | first5 = Anthony-Samuel | last5 = LaMantia | first6 = James O | last6 = McNamara | first7 = S Mark | last7 = Williams | name-list-format = vanc | title = Neuroscience | date = 2001 | publisher = Sinauer Associates | location = Sunderland, Mass | isbn = 978-0-87893-742-4 | edition = 2nd | chapter = Voltage-Gated Ion Channels | chapter-url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10883/ | access-date = 2020-10-14 | archive-date = 2018-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180605025823/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10883/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==结构==
[[File:Subunits_of_ion_channels_in_membrane.png|520px]]
电压门控离子通道的[[跨膜蛋白|跨膜区]]通常由几個同源结构域组成，这结构域在细胞膜上排列，让中间形成一个可开闭的孔道，可以使离子在[[电化学梯度|电化学梯度]]的作用下跨膜流动。这些通道通常是离子特异性的，每种通道只能通过特定离子，尽管大小相近、带电荷数相同的离子有时也会穿过它们<ref name="Bezanilla_2005">{{cite journal | vauthors = Bezanilla F | title = Voltage-gated ion channels | journal = IEEE Transactions on NanoBioscience | volume = 4 | issue = 1 | pages = 34–48 | date = March 2005 | pmid = 15816170 | doi=10.1109/tnb.2004.842463}}</ref>。 Na<sup>+</sup>、K<sup>+</sup>和Ca<sup>2+</sup>的通道都由四個同源结构域组成，这四個同源结构域以平面正方形排列，中间形成一个可让离子流动的孔道。其中大部分的Na<sup>+</sup>和Ca<sup>2+</sup>离子通道，四個同源结构域位于一条肽链上，而K<sup>+</sup>离子通道则是位于四条肽链上形成四聚体，如图<ref name="MCB_2000">{{cite book | first1 = Harvey | last1 = Lodish | first2 = Arnold | last2 = Berk | first3 = S Lawrence | last3 = Zipursky | first4 = Paul | last4 = Matsudaira | first5 = David | last5 = Baltimore | first6 = James | last6 = Darnell | name-list-style = vanc | title = Molecular Cell Biology | date = 2000 | publisher = Scientific American Books | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-7167-3136-8 | edition = 4th | chapter = Section 21.3, Molecular Properties of Voltage-Gated Ion Channels | chapter-url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK21608/ | url-access = registration | url = https://archive.org/details/molecularcellbio00lodi }}</ref>。跨膜区总共分为S1-S6六个由[[α螺旋|α螺旋]]组成的节段，其中第五个和第六个跨膜节段（S5和S6）形成了让离子通过的中心孔，其变构决定了离子通道的开关。而S1-S4节段为电压感应区，其中的S4节段的氨基酸残基带正电，感应跨膜电压的变化来变构调节S5和S6节段构象，从而使离子通道打开或关闭<ref name="Bezanilla_2005" />。上述跨膜蛋白可称为离子通道的α亚基，此外完整的离子通道还具有β调节亚基，具有[[氧化還原酶|氧化還原酶]]活性，定位于[[细胞皮层|细胞膜内侧]]而非跨膜，在[[内质网|内质网]]与α亚基组装在一起<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Gulbis JM, Mann S, MacKinnon R | title = Structure of a voltage-dependent K<sup>+</sup> channel beta subunit | journal = Cell | volume = 97 | issue = 7 | pages = 943–52 | date = June 1999 | pmid = 10399921 | doi=10.1016/s0092-8674(00)80805-3}}</ref>。

==机制==
离子通道中最早完成[[X射线晶体学|X射线晶体]]衍射图谱的是[[鉀離子通道|鉀離子通道]]，当细胞膜内外存在[[电压|电势差]]时，[[电场|电场]]会引起钾通道的构象变化。这种构象变化改变了通道蛋白的形状，使得四个同源结构域中的空腔通道打开，允许K<sup>+</sup>通过膜流入或流出。K<sup>+</sup>向着浓度低的移动，产生足以使细胞膜去极化的[[电流|电流]]。

电压门控钠离子通道和电压门控钙离子通道通常由带有四个同源结构域的单个肽链形成。每个同源结构域带有6个跨膜[[α-螺旋|α-螺旋]]，其中的S4节段涉及电压的感应<ref name="pmid20869590">{{cite journal | vauthors = Catterall WA | title = Ion channel voltage sensors: structure, function, and pathophysiology | journal = Neuron | volume = 67 | issue = 6 | pages = 915–28 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20869590 | pmc = 2950829 | doi = 10.1016/j.neuron.2010.08.021 }}</ref>。在钾通道和钠通道中，感应电压的S4节段富含[[赖氨酸|赖氨酸]]、[[精氨酸|精氨酸]]残基带有许多正电荷，因此细胞外的高正电会排斥该α-螺旋，从而使通道保持在闭合状态<ref name="Bezanilla_2005" />。

在[[静息电位|静息电位]]下，每个S4螺旋的一半与细胞胞浆接触。去极化后，外界电场减弱，S4节段上的带正电残基向膜的外表面移动<ref name="MCB_2000" /><ref name="Sands_2005">{{cite journal | vauthors = Sands Z, Grottesi A, Sansom MS | title = Voltage-gated ion channels | journal = Current Biology | volume = 15 | issue = 2 | pages = R44–7 | year = 2005 | pmid = 15668152 | doi = 10.1016/j.cub.2004.12.050 | doi-access = free }}</ref>，触发构象变化，从而打开通道<ref name="Bezanilla_2005" />。

[[File:130305-MGR-VSP_vs_VGIC_Schematic.png|thumb]]组成的]]
电压感应区的S3b节段S4节段在不同物种中[[保守序列|高度保守]]，且在多个物种的{{le|电压敏感磷酸酶|Voltage sensitive phosphatase}}的电压感应区中也存在类似的结构<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Murata Y, Iwasaki H, Sasaki M, Inaba K, Okamura Y | title = Phosphoinositide phosphatase activity coupled to an intrinsic voltage sensor | journal = Nature | volume = 435 | issue = 7046 | pages = 1239–43 | date = June 2005 | pmid = 15902207 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1038/nature03650 | bibcode = 2005Natur.435.1239M }}</ref>。沟过[[基因工程|基因工程]]将一种火山[[古菌|古菌]]的钾离子通道基因片段转入大鼠大脑中，发现转入的钾离子通道能正常工作<ref name="pmid18004375">{{cite journal | vauthors = Alabi AA, Bahamonde MI, Jung HJ, Kim JI, Swartz KJ | title = Portability of paddle motif function and pharmacology in voltage sensors | journal = Nature | volume = 450 | issue = 7168 | pages = 370–5 | date = November 2007 | pmid = 18004375 | pmc = 2709416 | doi = 10.1038/nature06266 | bibcode = 2007Natur.450..370A }}</ref><ref name="pmid18004376">{{cite journal | vauthors = Long SB, Tao X, Campbell EB, MacKinnon R | title = Atomic structure of a voltage-dependent K<sup>+</sup> channel in a lipid membrane-like environment | journal = Nature | volume = 450 | issue = 7168 | pages = 376–82 | date = November 2007 | pmid = 18004376 | doi = 10.1038/nature06265 | bibcode = 2007Natur.450..376L }}</ref>。

虽然电压门控离子通道通常是通过膜的[[去极化|去极化]]来激活的，但有些通道，如{{le|内向整流钾离子通道|Inward-rectifier potassium channel}}，是通过[[超极化_(生物学)|超极化]]来激活的。

在电压门控离子通道打开几毫秒后，离子通道会进入失活状态<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Armstrong CM | title = Sodium channels and gating currents | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_physiological-reviews_1981-07_61_3/page/644 | journal = Physiological Reviews | volume = 61 | issue = 3 | pages = 644–83 | date = July 1981 | pmid = 6265962 | doi = 10.1152/physrev.1981.61.3.644 }}</ref>。其中钾通道至少存在两种失活类型，即快速失活型（N型）和慢速失活型（C型）<ref>{{cite book |title=离子通道学 |publisher=Hu bei ke xue ji zhu chu ban she |location=Wu han |isbn=9787535238337}}</ref>。N型失活是一种{{le|球与链学说|ball and chain inactivation|“球与链”失活}}，在失活过程中，胞内区肽链会折叠起来，使得[[N-末端|N-末端]]的球会阻碍离子通过通道的流动<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Vassilev P, Scheuer T, Catterall WA | title = Inhibition of inactivation of single sodium channels by a site-directed antibody | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America | volume = 86 | issue = 20 | pages = 8147–51 | date = October 1989 | pmid = 2554301 | doi=10.1073/pnas.86.20.8147 | pmc=298232| bibcode = 1989PNAS...86.8147V }}</ref>。快速失活与S4节段膜内运动直接相关<ref name="Bénitah_1999">{{cite journal | vauthors = Bénitah JP, Chen Z, Balser JR, Tomaselli GF, Marbán E | title = Molecular dynamics of the sodium channel pore vary with gating: interactions between P-segment motions and inactivation | journal = The Journal of Neuroscience | volume = 19 | issue = 5 | pages = 1577–85 | date = March 1999 | pmid = 10024345 | pmc = 6782169 | doi = 10.1523/JNEUROSCI.19-05-01577.1999 }}</ref>。

==各种类型==

===钠离子（Na<sup href="electric field">+</sup>）通道===

[[钠离子通道|钠离子通道]]在许多不同的[[成人身体细胞类型列表|细胞类型]]中具有相似的功能特性。在[[人类基因组|人类基因组]]中有10个钠离子通道[[基因|基因]]，这些基因在进化中高度保守<ref name="Bénitah_1999" />。

===钙离子（Ca<sup>2+</sup>）通道===
人类基因组中共有16个不同的{{le|电压门控钙离子通道|Voltage-gated calcium channel}}基因，[[钙离子通道|钙离子通道]]在不同细胞类型中的功能不同。在一些[[神经元|神经元]]中Ca<sup>2+</sup>产生[[动作电位|动作电位]]的方式和Na<sup>+</sup>类似。钙通道也在[[神经末梢|神经末梢]]的{{le|化学突触|chemical synapse}}的[[胞吐作用|神经递质释放]]中起作用。 在大多数细胞中，Ca<sup>2+</sup>通道通过调控[[细胞内|细胞内]]Ca<sup>2+</sup>的浓度来调节各种各样的生化过程<<ref name="Jiang_2002">{{cite journal | vauthors = Jiang Y, Lee A, Chen J, Cadene M, Chait BT, MacKinnon R | title = Crystal structure and mechanism of a calcium-gated potassium channel | journal = Nature | volume = 417 | issue = 6888 | pages = 515–22 | date = May 2002 | pmid = 12037559 | doi = 10.1038/417515a | bibcode = 2002Natur.417..515J }}</ref>。

===钾离子（K<sup>+</sup>）通道===
[[电压门控钾离子通道|电压门控]][[鉀離子通道|鉀離子通道]]是电压门控通道中最大和最多样化的一类，在[[人类基因组|人类基因组]]中有超过100个基因。这些类型的通道在门控特性上有很大的不同；有些失活极慢，有些失活极快。这种激活时间的差异会影响[[动作电位|动作电位]]的持续时间和频率，这对[[轴突|轴突]]上的电信号传导以及突触传递有着重要的影响。钾通道与其他通道在结构上的不同之处在于它们包含四个独立的多肽亚基，而其他通道虽然也包含四个同源结构域，但只有一个多肽链<ref name="Sands_2005" />。

===氯离子（Cl<sup>−</sup>）通道===

{{le|氯离子通道|Chloride channel}}存在于所有类型的[[神经元|神经元]]中，主要负责控制细胞的兴奋性，有助于维持细胞[[静息电位|静息电位]]和调节细胞体积大小<ref name="Neuroscience_2001" />。

===质子（H<sup>+</sup>）通道===
{{le|电压门控质子通道|Voltage-gated proton channel}}是[[氢正离子|氢正离子]]的跨膜通道，并以[[pH|pH]]依赖的方式被去极化激活。它们的作用是除去细胞中的酸<ref>{{Citation|last1=Cherny|first1=V.V.|last2=Markin|first2=V.S.|last3=DeCoursey|first3=T.E.|publication-date=June 1995|title=The voltage-activated hydrogen ion conductance in rat alveolar epithelial cells is determined by the pH gradient|periodical=Journal of General Physiology|volume=105|issue=6|pages=861–896|doi=10.1085/jgp.105.6.861|pmid=7561747|pmc=2216954|year=1995}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=DeCoursey|first=T.E.|publication-date=2003|title=Voltage-gated proton channels and other proton transfer pathways|periodical=Physiological Reviews|volume=83|issue=2|pages=475–579|doi=10.1152/physrev.00028.2002|oclc=205658168|pmid=12663866|year=2003}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=An aqueous H<sup>+</sup> permeation pathway in the voltage-gated proton channel Hv1|first1=I. Scott|last1=Ramsey|first2=Younes|last2=Mokrab|first3=Ingrid|last3=Carvacho|first4=Zara A.|last4=Sands|first5=Mark S.P.|last5=Sansom|first6=David E.|last6=Clapham|journal=Nature Structural & Molecular Biology|volume=17|issue=7|pages=869–875|date=2010|doi=10.1038/nsmb.1826|pmid=20543828|pmc=4035905}}</ref>。

==系统进化==
{{further|阳离子通道超家族}}
2004年的一项[[系统发生学|系统发育]]研究发现细菌的[[电压门控钠离子通道|电压门控钠离子通道]]构成了一个[[蛋白质超家族|蛋白质超家族]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Koishi R, Xu H, Ren D, Navarro B, Spiller BW, Shi Q, Clapham DE | title = A superfamily of voltage-gated sodium channels in bacteria | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 279 | issue = 10 | pages = 9532–8 | date = March 2004 | pmid = 14665618 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.M313100200 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。之后多项研究将许多其它[[离子通道|离子通道]]和{{le|离子泵|Ion transporter}}与电压门控离子通道整合成一个系统发育树，包括{{le|内向整流钾离子通道|Inward-rectifier potassium ion channel}}、{{le|兰尼碱肌醇1,4,5-三磷酸受体钙通道|Ryanodine-Inositol 1,4,5-triphosphate receptor calcium channels}}、{{le|瞬时受体电位钙通道家族|Transient receptor potential calcium channel family}}、{{le|多囊蛋白阳离子通道家族|Polycystin cation channel family}}、{{le|谷氨酸门控离子通道家族|Glutamate-gated ion channel family}}、{{le|钙依赖性的氯离子通道|calcium-dependent chloride channel}}、{{le|单价阳离子：质子逆向转运蛋白-1|Monovalent cation:proton antiporter-1}}基因家族和{{le|钾转运蛋白家族|Potassium transporter family}}等<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Phylogeny as a guide to structure and function of membrane transport proteins|first1=Abraham B.|last1=Chang|first2=Ron|last2=Lin|first3=W. Keith|last3=Studley|first4=Can V.|last4=Tran|first5=Milton H., Jr.|last5=Saier|journal=Mol Membr Biol|date=2004|volume=21|issue=3|pages=171–181|doi=10.1080/09687680410001720830|pmid=15204625}}</ref>。

